high_descs: Go forward and stop to the left of the toilet.
Pick the bottle up from the back of the toilet.
Turn around and face the black table on the other side of the room.
Put the bottle on the black table to the left of the green spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a bottle on a table.

high_descs: Walk to the wall between the sink and the toilet.
Pick up the soap dispenser on the back of the toilet, above the handle.
Turn around and go to the black end table across the room.
Place the soap dispenser on the black table, to the left of the green spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put the spray bottle on the table.

high_descs: move to the bin to the right of the sink

move to the end table behind you
put the dispenser on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a dispenser on the end table.
